          <td height="45" VALIGN="TOP" bgcolor="#333333"><div class="topictitle"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width=100%>
      <tr>
       <td>
	   <div align="left" class="storytitle">DAoC Vegas Roundtable and Darkness Rising Preview</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By Aaron "Zato" Tarvin</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">Sep 26, 2005, 17:24</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=DAoC%20Vegas%20Roundtable%20and%20Darkness%20Rising%20Preview&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Farticles%2Fevents%2Farticle_34.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="http://www.thesafehouse.org/articles/events/printer_34.php">Printer&nbsp;friendly&nbsp;page</a></div>
	  <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="/cgi-bin/articles/exec/goforum.cgi?id=34&cat=26">Discuss this story</a></div>
	  </td>
      </tr>
     </table></div>
  
  
  </td>
</tr>
